name: Eugene Moore
description: i am down to earth, adventurous, and non-judgmental I believe in courtesy and civility – please, thank you, excuse me, Mr, Miss, Mrs are all in my vocabulary I have a great sense of humor – Almost too well developed – threatens people taking me seriously I am changeable and teachable – If you know a finer way I am willing to change – being hard headed doesn’t work very well I prefer to listen rather than talk, i like to hang around with friends, beach, hiking, biking was my fun, traveling, trying new things and more, pls no games, im too tired of that!!!
